CONTEXT CompositionISAheteroSubUnrelated IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT CompositionISAheteroSubUnrelated
{+ This test must fail because meet(A,C) does not exist.
   A and C are unrelated. +}

CLASSIFY A ISA B

RELATION r[W*A]
RELATION s[C*Z]
RELATION result[W*Z]

RULE testCompositionISAFail: result = r;s

ENDCONTEXT
